<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">9的倍数法，方法二，求123456789乘以小于90的9的倍数的积，得数就是除十位数字是0外，其余的数字都是n（9的倍数），共有9个。可用公式</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">123456789×(9n)=123456789×9×n=1111111101×n=nnnnnnnn0n</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中乘数为9n（n为小于10的自然数）</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">123456789×63=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 123456789×63</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=123456789×(9×7)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=123456789×9×7</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=7777777707</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>